rawContent:
I see absolutely no reason at all to play a Ubisoft game!

Ubisoft's venture into the Star Wars universe with "Outlaws" has been met with skepticism, not just for its gameplay mechanics or narrative, but also due to the broader context of fan dissatisfaction with how contemporary Star Wars projects have been handled in recent years (games, movies and shows).

Performance issues, mediocre gameplay and a perceived lack of innovation or engaging storytelling so it's a no for me.
